ation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out horizontally."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]}}}